                    <div class="example-response" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                        <h4>Next Steps:</h4>
                        <p>This self-explanation technique can be applied to any subject you're learning! Try it when reading textbooks, watching educational videos, or studying new skills. Simply pause regularly and ask yourself: "What does this mean? How does it connect to what I already know? Why is this important?"</p>
                    </div>

                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.1em; color: #666;">
                        Click below to explore another example or review this content again.
                    </p>
                `
            }
